mulberry (4.1.0a3-git-20260304-0035) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Modernization for Ubuntu 24.04 x86_64 with GCC 13 and OpenSSL 3.x
  * Compiler compatibility: removed deprecated register keyword, replaced
    std::auto_ptr with std::unique_ptr, changed throw() to noexcept
  * 64-bit fixes: corrected NumVersionVariant union size, fixed sentinel
    values for LP64 memory model
  * OpenSSL 3.x compatibility: migrated to opaque BIO API, updated
    deprecated function calls, added version guards for backward compatibility
  * Desktop integration: added .desktop file for application menu and
    mailto:/webcal: URL handler registration
  * SVN r515 patches: integrated local address book support and attendee
    dialog improvements from archived upstream repository
  * Timezone database: automated IANA tzdata integration via vzic
  * Bug fixes: preferences corruption defense, clipboard paste improvements,
    locale handling for 12-hour clock format
  * Security: added User-Agent header to HTTP requests matching email
    X-Mailer format

  [ Debian Packaging ]
  * Updated to Standards-Version 4.7.0.0 (from 3.8.3)
  * Migrated to debhelper compatibility level 13 (from 7)
  * Rewrote debian/rules using modern dh sequencer
  * Build flags: full hardening (including bindnow), LTO optimization,
    QA error checks for problematic code patterns
  * Added debian/copyright in DEP-5 machine-readable format
  * Added Homepage, Vcs-Git, and Vcs-Browser fields
  * Added AppStream metadata and desktop integration files
  * Improved package description with current features
  * Updated maintainer to reflect current maintenance
  * Removed bundled OpenSSL build, use system libssl-dev

 -- yitzhaq <github@anonmail.uk>  Wed, 04 Mar 2026 00:35:18 +0100

